wikipedia_page.main: Katie-Jemima Yeats-Brown (born 5 July 1995) is a British judoka who trains full-time at the British Judo Centre of Excellence in Walsall. She competed for England in the women's 63 kg event at the 2014 Commonwealth Games where she won a bronze medal.Katie-Jemima came 5th in the recent Senior World Championships in Baku and is currently ranked world 32 on IJF ranking list
